00:44:34.500 --> 00:44:36.154
All right so covariance.

00:44:36.154 --> 00:44:37.820
Covariance tells me
some measure of when

00:44:37.820 --> 00:44:41.250
x moves, how far does y move?
[? Or ?] for any other asset?

