00:46:57.180 --> 00:47:04.160
What this means, if I have a
covariance structure sigma.

00:47:04.160 --> 00:47:06.830
And I have a vector
of positions,

00:47:06.830 --> 00:47:10.430
x dollars in dollar/yen,
y dollars in gold,

00:47:10.430 --> 00:47:13.800
z dollars in oil.

